{"tid":1689174,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"部伏伏伏伏用無人機整落黎係咪得呢","createTime":"2019-11-02T17:01:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-05T05:40:11.000Z","uid":199606,"like":28,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"be113f28d81c30815ce0cc4d8628b6cf38ac63a9","tid":1689174,"uid":199606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T17:01:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XDvpsMq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXDvpsMq.png&h=2649af72&s={SIZE}\" />（電影節錄）<br />\n從理想值黎講 無人機帶住2kg既野撞佢條尾係有機會<br />\n無人機唔可以用膠個隻<br />\n之後就要計直昇機高度<br />\n今日直昇機係飛高過ifc<br />\nifc高度係412米<br />\n普通航拍機係可以飛高過412米<br />\n（講明先香港法例最高畀你飛120米）<br />\n直昇機主螺旋行既速率係大於200m/s<br />\n條件達成之後可以試下係部無人機<br />\n加繩啊加勁硬既野<br />\n<a href=\"https://dronephotographyservices.co.uk/can-small-drone-bring-helicopter/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdronephotographyservices.co.uk%2Fcan-small-drone-bring-helicopter%2F&d=5AUjfk%2BhgFT%2FKzSacqcGpKf05AUSLZuDOcHdeYvmXak%3D&h=776f75c4\" target=\"_blank\">https://dronephotographyservices.co.uk/can-small-drone-bring-helicopter/</a><br />\n但係只係從理想值咁講應該大概係可能<br />\n係咪真係得就唔知<br />\n咁至於部直昇機會點 照理咁撞完之後冇左尾翼<br />\n係絕對會不停旋轉之後失控<br />\n利申 9up唔鼓吹暴力犯法野<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c87b1fdc95e21ccb19cf4bc39d7a23c6c32ce24","tid":1689174,"uid":1255,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T17:06:00.000Z","msg":"十架無人機空中表演"},{"pid":"536a75fc5fc4d6e69d77d38c95370db7302d10a2","tid":1689174,"uid":199606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T17:10:14.000Z","msg":"理論<br />\n實質唔知"},{"pid":"19d26897a6be35877f25e979a48502f484625f6b","tid":1689174,"uid":199606,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7c87b1fdc95e21ccb19cf4bc39d7a23c6c32ce24","tid":1689174,"uid":1255,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T17:06:00.000Z","msg":"十架無人機空中表演"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T17:10:3